preference.name: METIMEPopulateAllocatedTimeUpToLevelEnabled
preference.preference_description: Specifies whether the option to update the allocated time to a certain level (Populate up to level) is active in the Populate Allocated Time dialog box in the Time pane. Valid Values: True - The Populate up to level option is available. False - The Populate up to level option is not available.
